hudson.plugins.git.GitChangeSetList","items":[{"_class":"hudson.plugins.git.GitChangeSet","affectedPaths":["Jenkinsfile"],"commitId":"9f0e99c8a7d4e06937d85486a80b614faea444cf","timestamp":1777535138000,"author":{"absoluteUrl":"http://localhost:8080/user/atul411","fullName":"atul411"},"authorEmail":"atul411@users.noreply.github.com","comment":"Replace Groovy helpers with env-var feature flags (sandbox-safe)\u000a\u000aThe previous credentialsExists()/isPluginInstalled() helpers used\u000aJenkins.instance and CredentialsProvider, which require admin approval\u000aunder Jenkins Script Security ('Scripts not permitted to use static\u000amethod jenkins.model.Jenkins getInstance'). Replaced with\u000asandbox-safe env-var gating:\u000a\u000a  ENABLE_SONAR=true        -> run SonarQube + Quality Gate stages\u000a  ENABLE_DOCKER_PUSH=true  -> run Docker Build + Push stages\u000a  ENABLE_DEPLOY=true       -> run Kubernetes deploy stage\u000a\u000aSet these in Jenkins → Manage Jenkins → System → Global properties\u000aor per-job parameters. With none set, the pipeline runs Checkout,\u000aSetup, Lint, Unit Tests only — green on a fresh Jenkins install.\u000aWith all three set, full pipeline through deploy.\u000a","date":"2026-04-30 13:15:38 +0530","id":"9f0e99c8a7d4e06937d85486a80b614faea444cf","msg":"Replace Groovy helpers with env-var feature flags (sandbox-safe)","paths":[{"editType":"edit","file":"Jenkinsfile"}]}],"kind":"git"}],"culprits":[{"absoluteUrl":"http://localhost:8080/user/atul411","fullName":"atul411"}],"inProgress":false,"nextBuild":{"number":8,"url":"http://localhost:8080/job/aceest-fitness/8/"},"previousBuild":{"number":6,"url":"http://localhost:8080/job/aceest-fitness/6/"}}